{"tid":1215324,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［有圖］我今次真係影到唯唯(唔係P圖)","createTime":"2019-06-13T06:46:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T06:55:39.000Z","uid":132414,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5058f950fe255d1eb23601566ec041d59af058d1","tid":1215324,"uid":132414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T06:46:50.000Z","msg":"之前啲post我都半信半疑<br />\n有張P圖出咗嚟之後簡直覺得屈佢嘅人無恥<br />\n但琴日我親眼見到佢<br />\n<br />\n612 下午3點鐘衝之前<br />\n唯唯就企係最前線<br />\n大家唔好再屈佢<br />\n佢係同香港企係同一陣線<br />\n<br />\n我知實會有人講叫唔好貼圖<br />\n但既然唯唯而都企得出嚟<br />\n我相信佢係真心用藝人嘅名義支持香港人<br />\n<br />\n唯唯好嘢！我怪咗錯你！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HRpMXqe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHRpMXqe.jpg&h=a20eb5cc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6f9404d51333e1b832e0ce365d15f80f7ff36aea","tid":1215324,"uid":8219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T06:47:50.000Z","msg":"唔好出樣呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df058a24193f4cf6fe695edde018e9f861f42934","tid":1215324,"uid":280,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T06:55:39.000Z","msg":"屌你....勁廢成個呀叔咁有大肚腩...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係都整張似D"}]}